“Thy to Aaba woh tmhre tum kia ho
  Hath per hath dharay Muntazir e farwa ho”

Ek larki ki awaz pr wah wah krny wali qoum ho gai hai humari..Astaghfirullah..ye kehna tha video ko sun k aur dekh k..
